## MuteState enum

Determines the mute state of the device, for the current call.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript

```

## Enumeration Members

|  Member | Value | Description |

|  MUTED | <code>&quot;muted&quot;</code> | The device is muted. |
|  NO\_ONGOING\_CALLS | <code>&quot;no-ongoing-calls&quot;</code> | The device cannot be muted or unmuted, as there are no ongoing calls right now. |
